    </a><a href="#whatmakesastronghumanresourcesbusinesspartner" class="cursor-pointer font-400 text-charcoal/70 inline-block text-[14px] leading-[24px] tracking-[0.1px] md:text-[16px] md:tracking-[0.15px]">2. What Makes a Strong Human Resources Business Partner?
    </a><a href="#whatisthedifferencebetweenanhrbusinesspartnerandanhrmanager" class="cursor-pointer font-400 text-charcoal/70 inline-block text-[14px] leading-[24px] tracking-[0.1px] md:text-[16px] md:tracking-[0.15px]">3. What is the difference between an HR Business Partner and an HR Manager?
    </a><a href="#hrbusinesspartner&#x2019;soretasks" class="cursor-pointer font-400 text-charcoal/70 inline-block text-[14px] leading-[24px] tracking-[0.1px] md:text-[16px] md:tracking-[0.15px]">4. HR Business Partner&#x2019;s Core Tasks
    </a><a href="#howcanyoushiftfromanhradministratortobusinesspartner" class="cursor-pointer font-400 text-charcoal/70 inline-block text-[14px] leading-[24px] tracking-[0.1px] md:text-[16px] md:tracking-[0.15px]">5. How Can You Shift From An HR Administrator To Business Partner?
    </a><a href="#conclusion" class="cursor-pointer font-400 text-charcoal/70 inline-block text-[14px] leading-[24px] tracking-[0.1px] md:text-[16px] md:tracking-[0.15px]">6. Conclusion
    </a></div></div></div> <div class="flair-container" data-v-3cb16c5a><div data-v-3cb16c5a><!----> <div data-v-3cb16c5a><article class="blog-markdown mx-auto max-w-screen-md prose prose-hr:h-[8px] prose-hr:m-0 prose-hr:border-none prose-headings:my-0 prose-headings:font-700 prose-headings:text-charcoal prose-h1:mb-[32px] prose-h1:mt-[48px] prose-h1:text-[34px] prose-h1:leading-[40px] prose-h1:tracking-[0.25px] md:prose-h1:text-[48px] md:prose-h1:leading-[56px] md:prose-h1:tracking-[0px] lg:prose-h1:text-[60px] lg:prose-h1:leading-[72px] prose-h2:text-[24px] prose-h2:leading-[32px] prose-h2:tracking-[0px] prose-h2:mt-[48px] prose-h2:mb-[24px] md:prose-h2:text-[34px] md:prose-h2:leading-[40px] md:prose-h2:tracking-[0.25px] lg:prose-h2:text-[40px] lg:prose-h2:leading-[48px] lg:prose-h2:tracking-[0px] prose-h3:text-[20px] prose-h3:leading-[32px] prose-h3:tracking-[0.15px] prose-h3:mb-[20px] md:prose-h3:text-[24px] md:prose-h3:leading-[32px] md:prose-h3:tracking-[0px] prose-p:m-0 prose-p:font-500 prose-p:text-charcoal prose-p:text-[14px] prose-p:leading-[24px] prose-p:tracking-[0.1px] prose-p:mb-[20px] md:prose-p:text-[16px] md:prose-p:leading-[32px] md:prose-p:tracking-[0.15px] prose-a:text-blue prose-strong:font-700 prose-blockquote:border-none prose-blockquote:relative prose-p:before:content-[] prose-blockquote:not-italic prose-blockquote:m-0 prose-blockquote:p-[8px_0px_8px_16px] md:prose-blockquote:p-[8px_0px_8px_26px] prose-blockquote:before:absolute prose-blockquote:before:inset-0 prose-blockquote:before:w-[4px] prose-blockquote:before:bg-blue prose-blockquote:before:rounded-full prose-blockquote:before:left-0 md:prose-blockquote:before:w-[6px] prose-ol:pl-[16px] prose-ol:mb-[20px] prose-ol:list-decimal md:prose-ol:pl-[26px] prose-li:marker:proportional-nums prose-ul:pl-[16px] prose-ul:mb-[20px] prose-ul:list-disc md:prose-ul:pl-[26px] prose-li:font-500 prose-li:text-charcoal prose-li:text-[16px] prose-li:leading-[32px] prose-li:m-0 prose-li:p-0 prose-table:table-fixed prose-table:border-[0px] prose-table:text-charcoal prose-table:text-[14px] prose-table:leading-[24px] md:prose-table:text-[16px] prose-tr:grid prose-tr:divide-y-[3px] prose-tr:divide-lavender prose-tr:border-[0px] sm:prose-tr:border-[3px] sm:prose-tr:border-lavender sm:prose-tr:table-row prose-td:p-[32px] sm:prose-td:border-[3px] sm:prose-td:border-lavender prose-th:p-[32px] empty:prose-th:hidden sm:empty:prose-th:table-cell sm:prose-th:border-[3px] sm:prose-th:border-lavender prose-thead:border-[3px] prose-thead:border-lavender prose-tbody:border-[3px] prose-tbody:border-lavender prose-tbody:divide-y-[3px] prose-tbody:divide-lavender"><h2 id="whatisahumanresourcebusinesspartner"><strong>What is a Human Resource Business Partner?</strong></h2>
<p>HRBPs are human resource experts whose primary role is to partner closely with a company&#x2019;s&#xA0;<strong>senior leadership</strong>&#xA0;to create an effective human resource plan.</p>
<p>This strategic plan should then be used to support the company&#x2019;s overall goals. Without a plan, the HR department may not be able to accomplish its goals as easily or understand which direction the company is moving.</p>
<p>A Human Resource business partner is also known as an&#xA0;<strong>alignment specialist</strong>&#xA0;who focuses on organizational strategy. As strategic business partners, the HRBPs help the business accomplish organizational goals and address strategic issues and business challenges.</p>
<p>The process might entail the HRBP working closely with the company board of directors or being present in board meetings.&#xA0;<strong>HRBPs are typically the most senior positions in human resources</strong>.</p>
<p>The business partner's roles are to deliver information to senior HR professionals routinely. They act as a direct link between the senior management of a company and the HR department.</p>
<p>Nowadays, HRBPs take on a new outlook in the&#xA0;<strong>current market landscape</strong>&#xA0;for people teams. They need to establish and build relationships and are also given a chance to take a counseling approach to human resources.</p>
<p>For instance, an employee may come to the human resources department when they need something; however, the key is to&#xA0;<strong>identify what they need</strong>. Therefore, an HRBP can guide them and, more essentially, help a company improve and engage their talent.</p>
<p>An HRBP can also be a strategic partner. A strategic business partner is a leader who is included in all conversations about the company's business objectives, future, and overall HR strategy. However, you must have some skills to become a strategic HR business partner.</p>
<h2 id="whatmakesastronghumanresourcesbusinesspartner">What Makes a Strong Human Resources Business Partner?</h2>
<p>The role of the HRBP is now more significant than ever, and there are many demands to improve its value. Also, many business partners are coming to terms with the fact that they can make a big difference to their company's profitability by&#xA0;<strong>making good use of their people</strong>.</p>
</article></div> <!----> <!----></div><div data-v-3cb16c5a><!----> <!----> <div data-v-3cb16c5a><div class="max-w-screen-lg mx-auto my-[20px] min-h-[180px] h-[180px] overflow-hidden rounded-[5px] md:min-h-[340px] md:h-[340px] lg:min-h-[400px] lg:h-[400px] md:rounded-[10px] lg:my-[40px] inner-img:w-full inner-img:h-full inner-img:object-cover" data-v-3cb16c5a><picture><source media="(min-width: 1280px)" type="image/webp" data-srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/1336x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/1074x400/b5142a8a90/02_flair_hr-partner_hr-responsibilities.png 1x, https://img2.storyblok.com/2672x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/1074x400/b5142a8a90/02_flair_hr-partner_hr-responsibilities.png 2x" srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/1336x0/filters:format(webp):blur(30):quality(30)/f/145847/1074x400/b5142a8a90/02_flair_hr-partner_hr-responsibilities.png, https://img2.storyblok.com/2672x0/filters:format(webp):blur(30):quality(30)/f/145847/1074x400/b5142a8a90/02_flair_hr-partner_hr-responsibilities.png 2x"><source media="(min-width: 1024px)" type="image/webp" data-srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/1176x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/1074x400/b5142a8a90/02_flair_hr-partner_hr-responsibilities.png 1x, https://img2.storyblok.com/2352x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/1074x400/b5142a8a90/02_flair_hr-partner_hr-responsibilities.png 2x" srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/1176x0/filters:format(webp):blur(30):quality(30)/f/145847/1074x400/b5142a8a90/02_flair_hr-partner_hr-responsibilities.png, https://img2.storyblok.com/2352x0/filters:format(webp):blur(30):quality(30)/f/145847/1074x400/b5142a8a90/02_flair_hr-partner_hr-responsibilities.png 2x"><source media="(min-width: 768px)" type="image/webp" data-srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/920x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/1074x400/b5142a8a90/02_flair_hr-partner_hr-responsibilities.png 1x, https://img2.storyblok.com/1840x0/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/1074x400/b514